Summary: 3 orange lights hovered in sky. Then disappeared.
trends: There has been one other sighting in Otsego
There were no other sightings in Otsego on or around October 12th 2013
divs: Sighting DetailsWe were driving home from a movie theater. My younger brother said, what are those orange lights in the sky. My girlfriend and I looked up and saw 3 orange lights in the air. The lights were orange and stationary. As we drove down the road the lights didn't move. Minutes later the triangle of orange lights disappeared. I'm not sure what the lights were!
